# Ignore the "runs" directory, but force the submission of the ".bit" and ".dcp" files under "runs/impl_1".              忽略.runs目录，但强制提交runs/impl_1下的.bit和.dcp文件
*.runs/*
!*.runs/impl_1/
*.runs/impl_1/*
!*.runs/impl_1/*.bit
!*.runs/impl_1/*.dcp